"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-06-parisolympics-clayton-salmon-womens-400m-hurdles-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"KINGSTON, Jamaica- National champion Rushell Clayton and Shiann Salmon are through to the final of the women's 400m hurdles, one of the most highly anticipated events on the track and field schedule at the Olympic games, after Tuesday's semi-finals at Stade de France in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rushell_Clayton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rushell Clayton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rushell_Clayton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rushell_Clayton\"}, {\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiann_Salmon\", \"score\": 0.9999999936123913, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shiann Salmon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiann_Salmon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiann_Salmon\"}, {\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999961353866735, \"rank\": 3.864628266241211e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clayton won her semi-final heat in 53.00 seconds to take an automatic qualifying spot, while Salmon ran a lifetime best 53.13 seconds to advance on time.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two-time Olympic finalist Janieve Russell however failed to advance to the final, as she was fourth in her semi-final race in 54.65 seconds.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janieve_Russell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janieve Russell\", \"